  "title": "De Morgan's Laws",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $U$ be a universe and $A,B \\subseteq U$. Then\n\\[\n(A \\cup B)^c = A^c \\cap B^c\n\\quad\\text{and}\\quad\n(A \\cap B)^c = A^c \\cup B^c.\n\\]",
